entries.meaning:
(mathematics) A statement that of two quantities one is specifically less than (or greater than) another. Symbol: 



        <


    {\displaystyle <}

 or 



        ≤


    {\displaystyle \leq }

 or 



        >


    {\displaystyle >}

 or 



        ≥


    {\displaystyle \geq }

 or 



        ≠


    {\displaystyle \neq }

, as appropriate.
